OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain clearing to the south during the
OL,7,Fevening, leaving the region with clear
OL,8,Fspells. Chilly with a touch of grass
OL,9,Ffrost in the rural north.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FAfter a chilly start, there
OL,12,Fwill be plenty of dry and bright
OL,13,Fweather around on Sunday. Light winds
OL,14,Fand temperatures below average for
OL,15,Fearly to mid-May.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
